   DISCLAIMER: While the information presented on this web site is deemed
      accurate as of the date of publication, it should not be cited or
     relied upon as legal authority. Any legal advice should be obtained
    from an attorney or legal association. For filing requirements please
     refer to the Federal Rules of Civil Procedure, the Federal Rules of
   Criminal Procedure, and the Local Rules for the United States District
                  Court for the Southern District of Ohio.
